{
  "stem": "7069.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At least now finally we got some fresh air as the doors were-- doors were opened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We that could, were able to hop out, hopped out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And others were laying down there, didn't move.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we figured it's the best to leave them there, maybe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we were lined up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after standing there for a while, the chief there, the guy with his megaphone, goes, well, he says, we understand that because of an oversight, you didn't get any food.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We want you to understand that there is food waiting for you in the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We are now on the entrance ramp of Auschwitz-Birkenau, the long entrance ramp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You see some pictures of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The train is on this side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The other side is open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There's-- there were these guys, the, the, the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Their troops were lined up on the other side of the ramp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so he says, there's food waiting for you in the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But before we, we can take you into the camp, there are some items that have to be taken care of.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the faster you will be comply with that, the faster you will do the things that we ask you to do, the sooner you will be in camp and have your food.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So therefore, we want you to understand that whatever we do, if you hurry up, you get your food very soon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first thing we have to do is that because of the fact that you have to work from morning to evening, very late and long hours, you-- I, I see that many of you have, have here small children.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm talking about the children of 13 and under, which, which it was at that point.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were other ages at certain other times.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
